      <data key="d0">TERM</data>
      <data key="d1">Ph&#7851;u thu&#7853;t tim l&#224; c&#225;c can thi&#7879;p ph&#7851;u thu&#7853;t v&#224;o tim, c&#243; th&#7875; &#273;&#7875; l&#7841;i v&#7871;t s&#7865;o v&#224; g&#226;y ra r&#7889;i lo&#7841;n nh&#7883;p th&#7845;t sau ph&#7851;u thu&#7853;t.</data>
