    <edge source="R&#7888;I LO&#7840;N NH&#7882;P TH&#7844;T" target="T&#193;C D&#7908;NG PH&#7908; C&#7910;A THU&#7888;C">
      <data key="d8">8.0</data>
      <data key="d9">M&#7897;t s&#7889; lo&#7841;i thu&#7889;c c&#243; th&#7875; g&#226;y ra r&#7889;i lo&#7841;n nh&#7883;p th&#7845;t nh&#432; t&#225;c d&#7909;ng ph&#7909;, &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t &#7903; b&#7879;nh nh&#226;n c&#243; y&#7871;u t&#7889; nguy c&#417;.</data>
      <data key="d10">8450452994017d98ea3f4f54219b67d8</data>
      <data key="d11">efc335621de5410f8bfa8f7de5eb2c74</data>
