    <edge source="R&#7888;I LO&#7840;N NH&#7882;P TH&#7844;T" target="TRI&#7878;T &#272;&#7888;T R&#7888;I LO&#7840;N NH&#7882;P">
      <data key="d8">9.0</data>
      <data key="d9">Tri&#7879;t &#273;&#7889;t r&#7889;i lo&#7841;n nh&#7883;p l&#224; ph&#432;&#417;ng ph&#225;p &#273;i&#7873;u tr&#7883; can thi&#7879;p hi&#7879;u qu&#7843; cho c&#225;c tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p r&#7889;i lo&#7841;n nh&#7883;p th&#7845;t.</data>
      <data key="d10">e8614181c1c96a52140d67b12b26678f</data>
      <data key="d11">247ff19a8e454f5d937955f4ffa85e87</data>
      <data key="d12">21</data>
