    <edge source="R&#7888;I LO&#7840;N NH&#7882;P TH&#7844;T" target="C&#7844;Y M&#193;Y PH&#193; RUNG T&#7920; &#272;&#7896;NG">
      <data key="d8">1.0</data>
      <data key="d9">C&#7845;y m&#225;y ph&#225; rung t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng l&#224; bi&#7879;n ph&#225;p theo d&#245;i v&#224; &#273;i&#7873;u tr&#7883; r&#7889;i lo&#7841;n nh&#7883;p th&#7845;t nguy hi&#7875;m.</data>
      <data key="d10">e8614181c1c96a52140d67b12b26678f</data>
