    <edge source="R&#7888;I LO&#7840;N NH&#7882;P TH&#7844;T" target="TRI&#7878;U CH&#7912;NG R&#7888;I LO&#7840;N NH&#7882;P TH&#7844;T">
      <data key="d8">9.0</data>
      <data key="d9">Tri&#7879;u ch&#7913;ng r&#7889;i lo&#7841;n nh&#7883;p th&#7845;t l&#224; c&#225;c bi&#7875;u hi&#7879;n m&#224; b&#7879;nh nh&#226;n c&#243; th&#7875; g&#7863;p ph&#7843;i khi m&#7855;c ph&#7843;i t&#236;nh tr&#7841;ng n&#224;y, &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng &#273;&#7871;n ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng cu&#7897;c s&#7889;ng.</data>
      <data key="d10">e8614181c1c96a52140d67b12b26678f</data>
